<inglise> 9. </inglise>
<eesti> 9. </eesti>
<inglise> A Member shall notify to the General Council the introduction of or any changes in the application of restrictive import measures taken for balance-of-payments purposes, as well as any modifications in time-schedules for the removal of such measures as announced under paragraph 1. </inglise>
