<inglise> Members which have reasons to believe that a restrictive import measure applied by another Member was taken for balance-of-payments purposes may bring the matter to the attention of the Committee. </inglise>
<eesti> Liikmed, kel on p&otilde;hjust arvata, et piirav impordimeede, mida teine liige on rakendanud, on v&otilde;etud seoses maksebilansiga, v&otilde;ivad juhtida sellele k&uuml;simusele komitee t&auml;helepanu. </eesti>
<inglise> The Chairman of the Committee shall request information on the measure and make it available to all Members. </inglise>
